item.title: JWA
item.description: JWA - Jadam Wetting Agent Lantern And Goblin Jadam Wetting agent is a natural emulsifier and wetting agent that breaks down completely in 72hrs. Not using synthetic foaming and wetting agents help protect the waterways by not letting the synthetic soaps and foaming agents into those waterways. Not only the Jadam wetting agent breaks down naturally in the soil even though itâ€™s not recommended to water indirectly but drips and drops falling of the plant from a foliar application is nothing to worry about.
